title: Tyreek Blockbuster Breakdown + Liar Liar, FA Updates! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 3/24
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason react to Tyreek Hill being traded to the Dolphins! What’s the fantasy football fallout for Patrick Mahomes? How about Jaylen Waddle and Tua? Plus, more free agent signings to report and a fun game of “Liar Liar!” Follow now for fantasy content all offseason! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for March 24th, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(02:40) - Tyreek Hill Traded to Dolphins
(18:55) - Leonard Fournette
(20:20) - Jamison Crowder
(22:00) - Liar, Liar!
(35:30) - Mailbag
(36:20) - Travis Kelce or CeeDee Lamb?
(38:00) - Lamar Jackson Dynasty Value
(42:55) - Drop Antonio Brown?
(44:40) - Ezekiel Elliott Dynasty Value
(47:10) - Jimmy Garoppolo
